## Verifying this release

This release is signed end-to-end with [Sigstore](https://www.sigstore.dev/) keyless signing.

### Verify the Git tag

The `${TAG_NAME}` tag is signed with [gitsign](https://github.com/sigstore/gitsign):

```sh
gitsign verify-tag \
  --certificate-identity="${CERTIFICATE_IDENTITY}" \
  --certificate-oidc-issuer="https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com" \
  ${TAG_NAME}
```

### Verify the release images

The exact image digests built for this release are attached to this GitHub
release as `*.digest.json` assets. The images themselves are signed with cosign
keyless signing. To verify the frontend image for this release with
[cosign](https://github.com/sigstore/cosign):

```sh
cosign verify ghcr.io/${IMAGE_REPO}/frontend:${IMAGE_TAG} \
  --certificate-oidc-issuer="https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com" \
  --certificate-identity="https://github.com/${IMAGE_REPO}/.github/workflows/frontend-image.yml@refs/tags/${TAG_NAME}"
```

See the [image verification guide](https://project-dalec.github.io/dalec/verifying-images)
for worker images and `gh attestation verify` instructions.

### Verify the digest manifests

Each `*.digest.json` asset records the exact image digest built for this
release and is itself signed with cosign keyless signing. The signature is
attached as a matching `*.digest.json.cosign.bundle` asset. To verify a digest
manifest (for example `frontend.digest.json`):

```sh
cosign verify-blob frontend.digest.json \
  --bundle frontend.digest.json.cosign.bundle \
  --certificate-oidc-issuer="https://token.actions.githubusercontent.com" \
  --certificate-identity="https://github.com/${IMAGE_REPO}/.github/workflows/frontend-image.yml@refs/tags/${TAG_NAME}"
```

Worker digest manifests are signed by `worker-images.yml`; substitute that
workflow in the `--certificate-identity` value when verifying them.
